articles.title: About this site
articles.contents:
This website is intended to share my experiences and projects
regarding Applied Mathematics and Statistics!

articles.title: Nicholas Di's Portfolio
articles.description: Applied Mathmatics/Statistics and Economics Double Major at Macalester College
articles.contents:
Picture of Nicholas DiGreetings, welcome to my portfolio! I am a double major in Economics
and Applied Math/Statistics at Macalester college. I am particularly
interested in Econometrics and Probability/Statistics theory. Outside of
school, I enjoy going to the gym, reading, and skiing!
